Race.SpecificTitle: Alderman -- at Large, Town of Simmesport
PW Prop. No. 1 -- 6.20 Mills - PJ - 10 yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide Propositions
Proposition No. 1
(Library Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Avoyelles, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a six and twenty hundredths (6.20) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $837,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of providing necessary funds for the maintenance and support of the Avoyelles Parish public libraries?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Prop. No. 2 -- 3-1/2 Mills - PJ - 10 yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Avoyelles, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a three and one-half (3-1/2) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $472,500 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of providing necessary funds for drainage maintenance and improvements in the Parish?
